        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/avitus/{size}/34172_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-08-03T15:39:00.065Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"soderholm\" data-post=\"1\" data-topic=\"70820\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/da6949/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"> soderholm:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Add a subtle but clear visual indicator on the main chat list when a contact has posted a story, without requiring the user to enter the chat thread or head to the stories tab.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>There is an indicator on the main chat list on the Stories tab. Stories are only viewable from the Stories tab. If they were in a given conversation they‚Äôd just be a media message that might or might not disappear depending on disappearing messages settings.</p>\n<details>\n<summary>\nAndroid</summary>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/7/e/7e0df6e0969df906fc30632fedab94ed3e884a85.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/7e0df6e0969df906fc30632fedab94ed3e884a85\" title=\"1000010066\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/e/7e0df6e0969df906fc30632fedab94ed3e884a85_2_690x95.jpeg\" alt=\"1000010066\" data-base62-sha1=\"hZ84WI3kYsukgUoHrQGm2wvSE0B\" width=\"690\" height=\"95\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/e/7e0df6e0969df906fc30632fedab94ed3e884a85_2_690x95.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/e/7e0df6e0969df906fc30632fedab94ed3e884a85_2_1035x142.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/7/e/7e0df6e0969df906fc30632fedab94ed3e884a85_2_1380x190.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"E8EAF1\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">10000100