        "created_at": "2025-08-03T17:43:11.545Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I think more what‚Äôs being suggested is to make the chat page consistent with the thread view. At the moment, if a contact has a story, when you are chatting with them you can see this with a circle around their profile picture:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/5/c599e3cd59fe654f583456373e319f01530d0100.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/c599e3cd59fe654f583456373e319f01530d0100\" title=\"signal-2025-07-30-190442_002\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/5/c599e3cd59fe654f583456373e319f01530d0100_2_690x103.png\" alt=\"signal-2025-07-30-190442_002\" data-base62-sha1=\"sc3LGFPeEaaRy9Xo7t4za45ZB6g\" width=\"690\" height=\"103\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/5/c599e3cd59fe654f583456373e319f01530d0100_2_690x103.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/c/5/c599e3cd59fe654f583456373e319f01530d0100_2_1035x154.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/c/5/c599e3cd59fe654f583456373e319f01530d0100.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"23262C\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">signal-2025-07-30-190442_002</span><span class=\"informations\">1280√ó192 24.7 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>However, on the chat view there is no such indicator:</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/8/a843742f3aeba51cc8edb0b57606c140f2d4c2ff.png\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/a843742f3aeba51cc8edb0b57606c140f2d4c2ff\" title=\"signal-2025-07-30-190505_002\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/8/a843742f3aeba51cc8edb0b57606c140f2d4c2ff_2_224x499.png\" alt=\"signal-2025-07-30-190505_002\" data-base62-sha1=\"o0wJwolI1A5QL8Bz3pLztAd8bJt\" width=\"224\" height=\"499\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/8/a843742f3aeba51cc8edb0b57606c140f2d4c2ff_2_224x499.png, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/8/a843742f3aeba51cc8edb0b57606c140f2d4c2ff_2_336x748.png 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/8/a843742f3aeba51cc8edb0b57606c140f2d4c2ff_2_448x998.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"191A1E\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">signal-2025-07-30-190505_002</span><span class=\"informations\">1280√ó2856 146 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Sure, as mentioned, there‚Äôs the indicator under stories but during day-to-day usage it is far from where the eye is drawn at a glance. I personally would find it useful to have the same indicator on the chat page. At the very least it would be nice for the profile picture interactions to be consistent.</p>",
