        "created_at": "2025-08-03T19:31:02.208Z",
        "cooked": "<p>True but that‚Äôs for all contacts and the indicator commonly missed by users.</p>\n<p>My own partner regularly misses my own stories and uses the app multiple times a day.</p>\n<p>The main listing page only holds all your current conversations so presumably these are people you‚Äôd want to see stories of, not the full list available via the stories tab.</p>",
