      {
        "id": 273463,
        "name": "",
        "username": "soderholm",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/da6949/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2025-08-14T10:47:47.518Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Yeah lots of my contacts are over social media in its current form as this feature is just enough to replicate that original experience we all miss, just make it a little more clear that the content is there and watch engagement increase.</p>\n<p>I‚Äôve had this feedback from multiple people saying they miss my stories and wish they could see them.</p>\n<p>As mentioned those who don‚Äôt want stories can simply disable them.</p>",
